\nw[\N[21]]I've never seen anything like it, and it looks
strong...

\nw[Prae's voice]Is that... a demon from the demon realm...? This
is bad, the gate might be open.

\nw[Prae's voice]Hurry up and go to the temple. If we get attacked
by something like that, there's nothing we can do.
Now is not the time to go back.
Now is not the time to go back.

\nw[\N[1]]Is that so!? Alright, I understand. I'll hurry and
head there!
